{"version":1,"entries":{"person_2084573_translations":{"at":1774722342689,"data":{"id":2084573,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Sun Qian is a Chinese mainland actress, born in 1997 in Harbin, and a graduate of the Central Academy of Drama. Before pursuing acting, she trained in ballet for seven years at the high school affiliated with the Beijing Dance Academy. In May 2017, she gained recognition for starring as Shi Miao in the live-action adaptation of the popular Chinese comic \"Take My Brother Away.\"","name":"Sun Qian","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"孙千，1997年出生，中国内地女演员。\n\n2016年，孙千因参演电影处女作《我的青春都是你》而正式进入演艺圈。2017年，主演根据幽灵姐妹同名国漫改编的青春校园偶像剧《快把我哥带走》。2018年，主演都市青春励志剧《我在未来等你》；7月9日，参演的根据神尾叶子漫画《花样男子》改编的青春言情偶像剧《流星花园》首播；同年11月，主演青春偶像剧《淑女飘飘拳》。2020年，主演的古装言情喜剧《萌医甜妻》和都市青春言情剧《拾光里的我们》先后上线。","name":"孙千","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"손천","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tôn Thiến","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"孫千","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сунь Цянь","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"孫千，1997 年出生，中國內地女演員。\n\n2016 年，孫千因參演電影處女作《我的青春都是你》而正式進入演藝圈。2017 年，主演根據幽靈姐妹同名國漫改編的青春校園偶像劇《快把我哥帶走》。2018 年，主演都市青春勵志劇《我在未來等你》；7 月 9 日，參演的根據神尾葉子漫畫《花樣男子》改編的青春言情偶像劇《流星花園》首播；同年 11 月，主演青春偶像劇《淑女飄飄拳》。2020 年，主演的古裝言情喜劇《萌醫甜妻》和都市青春言情劇《拾光裏的我們》先後上線。","name":"孫千","primary":false}}]}},"person_4661648_translations":{"at":1774722348123,"data":{"id":4661648,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"